import React from 'react'
import { Wrapper, About, AboutTitle, PICont, MeCont, SkillsCont,
Title, MeBody, Image } from '../Components/AboutMe/AboutMe.elements'
import image from '../AustinMap.PNG'

function AboutPage() {
  return (
    <About  id='AboutMe'>
      <AboutCont>
        <AboutTitle>About Me</AboutTitle>
        <PICont>
          <MeCont>
            <Title>Who am I?</Title>
            <MeBody>
              I am a Software Developer based in Austin, TX. 
            </MeBody>
            
              <Image src={image} />
            
          </MeCont>
          <SkillsCont>
            Skills
          </SkillsCont>
        </PICont>
      </AboutCont>
    </About>
  )
}

export default AboutPage
